\pard\f0\fs28  {\b V. accrescens} Klokov in Klokov & Wissjul.,{\i  Fl. RSS Ucr.}{\b  7}: 632 (1955), from Ukraine and S. Russia, is like {\b 23} but has larger stems and leaves, papillose stems and petioles, and usually white flowers.
